OL,5,G0345 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,6,     FHelen has a new woman in her life
OL,7,     Fand Gus is about to get a woman in
OL,8,     Fhis life as Cupid starts firing
OL,9,     Fpoison-tipped arrows.
OL,10,G0410 Drop The Dead Donkey
